>\nO'er the land of the free and the home of the brave?<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">背熟第一段</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">叫英文口號</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Five demands Not one less</span><br />\n香港警察 知法犯法<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Hong Kong Police breaking the peace</span><br />\n與港同在 促成人權法案<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Stand with Hong Kong, pass the democracy act</span><br />\n為自由抗爭 制度已失衡<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Fight for freedom, no faith in the systems</span> </strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">應對記者資料</span></span><br />\n<br />\n[置頂][行動] 9月8點應對外國記者+3首歌歌詞+資料整合<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1551469\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1551469</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c6d8afb114355182b9ebaec1f8476d9316eda24c","tid":1551544,"uid":34777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T05:05:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"db90368b17f270d6b201eae6b465fde36ffd2504","tid":1551544,"uid":34777,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T05:05:18.000Z","msg":"靚女呀屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7410cb033282d0c6664c97a009d81001bc1805b5","tid":1551544,"uid":74929,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T05:05:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W16DxAR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW16DxAR.jpg&h=6b663e35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B1mTkZ7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB1mTkZ7.jpg&h=106f1e65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/09/08/121821_334341e1fd8cd0795176f952631cddf0.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.